{"tid":2199216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「民主運動啟發世界」 港人奪自由之家年獎","createTime":"2020-09-12T04:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T04:41:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"444531fc4ffd1d4260b091ba2e7a7597caae6500","tid":2199216,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/AWQTUMWSRZGNBEHY5OEMNTDT6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FAWQTUMWSRZGNBEHY5OEMNTDT6U%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f7Hzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=ad270b6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FAWQTUMWSRZGNBEHY5OEMNTDT6U%2F&h=e85e09b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/AWQTUMWSRZGNBEHY5OEMNTDT6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「民主運動啟發世界」<br />\n港人奪自由之家年獎<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港人持續捍衞應有的權利與自由，再次獲得國際民權機構的肯定。支持民主發展的美國著名非政府組織「自由之家」（Freedom House）公佈年度獎項，「香港民主運動」是三個得獎單位之一。本港抗爭人士認為，獲獎顯示港人追求的價值觀獲全世界認同、努力獲得肯定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uvQmTVQxh21_SvaquzZ-wK6k0Eg=/2362x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IROHTRK77RFCZIAFCJZ7OHZUPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuvQmTVQxh21_SvaquzZ-wK6k0Eg%3D%2F2362x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIROHTRK77RFCZIAFCJZ7OHZUPA.jpg&h=0e510015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■羅冠聰獲邀下周三在頒獎禮透過視像發言。羅冠聰fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰獲邀頒獎禮發言<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。大會指，在中國政府對內加強壓制、對外輸出威權主義下，「沒有領袖、民眾自發的香港民主運動啟發了全世界，200萬人上街捍衞香港法律下應有的自由與權利」。<br />\n<br />\n大會又指北京突然強推國安法，令港人的努力受到嚴重威脅，但「港人仍然致力於以新穎有創意的方法保衞下一代的權利」。身在海外為香港「打國際線」的羅冠聰，獲邀下周三透過視像在頒獎禮發言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XaTR7KKs-w0FvPEI14X-ty7jWqY=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6UHL6QCOOBGZNE56DA6IMWS6MY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXaTR7KKs-w0FvPEI14X-ty7jWqY%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6UHL6QCOOBGZNE56DA6IMWS6MY.jpg&h=65d33b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港人堅持抗爭捍衞權利與自由，獲國際社會肯定。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n另外同時獲獎的「蘇丹專業聯會」及蘇丹「12月革命烈士家庭組織」亦是致力推動和平示威、要求政府民主而和平地交接。<br />\n<br />\n香港民間人權陣線召集人岑子杰向本報表示，獲獎反映香港人過去一年追求的價值觀獲全世界認同，獲獎變相聲援香港民主運動。前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒則讚曾多次被中共點名制裁的自由之家「面對中共威脅仍沒放棄關注香港」；而今次是港版國安法實施以來，香港人首獲國際知名組織獎項，香港人努力再獲肯定。<br />\n<br />\n曾訪美交流反映香港情況的公民黨譚文豪認為，獎項屬於「全香港人，特別係喺反修例事件中犧牲好多嘅香港人」。議會陣線毛孟靜指自由之家是歷史悠久的國際民權機構，港人獲獎反映本港民主運動即使「本地有人唔認同，但喺外國係有人認同」，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"65b6083510bb2bae2a981a42cb1d39068c4250df","tid":2199216,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12:15 updates retweet link<br />\n<br />\n國務院<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1304561902396346373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1304561902396346373&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f7Hzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=0fc646f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1304561902396346373&h=9dad289f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1304561902396346373</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/statedeptspox/status/1304562964666744833?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstatedeptspox%2Fstatus%2F1304562964666744833%3Fs%3D21&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f7Hzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=e1b07b75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstatedeptspox%2Fstatus%2F1304562964666744833%3Fs%3D21&h=1ef8769c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/statedeptspox/status/1304562964666744833?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n